snippet.title: The Evidence - Trailer [PC/Steam]
snippet.description:
In The Evidence you'll take over the role of a detective who has to search for evidence at crime scenes and identify the possible murderer. Use your sharp mind and find the connections to solve the case!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2075880
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TMD_Interactive
